name: Blue_Mint5
description: Loose sketches of girl figures caught in a flow of emotions. A bit of hope on top of resignation, hesitation and melancholy. Exploration of flow, hand drawing, fast sketches and visible paint strokes. Created fully digitally in Photoshop. Mint 5 (out of 6) Edition of 5.  Mint 5 is the least figurative one - Girl sketches are broken with a geometric pattern that draws away the attention, this is the experimental mint.  Warsaw, FuzOne 30 04 2021
